item.title: David Lynch Continues to Haunt American Culture, Onscreen and On Canvas
item.description:
David Lynch Continues to Haunt American Culture, Onscreen and On Canvas

Everyone knows that from 1977 to 2006, David Lynch was responsible for many of the oddest, most imaginative movies and television series in American entertainment history: Eraserhead, Twin Peaks, Blue Velvet, Mulholland Drive, Elephant Man-the list goes on.
